Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.51,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:25.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}狰狞无比的凄惨之战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}爱总是无法无天的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}仅属于我的放荡之战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那句再见  无法说出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:37.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我真是没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:39.50,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我不明白  我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}搞不明白自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:47.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这份心情无法释怀  无法割舍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:52.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}越是想着不可以  就陷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:57.75,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}变得连自己都开始怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:01.35,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不如相信它
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:05.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管会失去什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:08.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都决定要伴随在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:09.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:12.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:14.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就算到了明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:17.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I want you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:19.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}命运要我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.63,0:01:25.09,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}要我止步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:27.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\fnDFGSoGei-W7\fs21}I cannot stop because I need you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:29.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}这理由却还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:34.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我可为你抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:35.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你一起极限战斗
